compute_mean <- function(data, scales){
  
  data %>% 
    summarise(x = mean(x),
              y = mean(y))
  
}

########  groupwise computation via compute group ####

Experiment

library(tidyverse)

compute_mean <- function(data, ...){
  
  data %>% 
    distinct(PANEL) ->
  panel_df
  
  data %>% 
    summarise(x = mean(x),
              y = mean(y)) %>% 
    crossing(panel_df)
      
  
}

########  groupwise computation via compute group ####
StatMeanlayer <- ggproto(`_class` = "StatMeanlayer",
                         `_inherit` = Stat,
                         compute_layer = compute_mean)

ggplot(cars) + 
  aes(speed, dist) + 
  geom_point(size = .15) +
  layer(geom = "point", 
        stat = StatMeanlayer, 
        position = "identity")

last_plot() +
  facet_wrap(facets = vars(speed > 10)) 

layer_data(i = 2)
